type: ENGINEERING DESIGN SERVICES FOR WHITBY HAVOUR SEDIMENT MANAGEMENT PROJECT
short_summary: Preparation of the Detailed Engineering Design for the implementation of the Whitby Harbour Remediation Project in the Whitby Small Craft Harbour.
description: Engineering Design Services for sediment management in Whitby. The Consultant firm to prepare the Detailed Engineering Design for the implementation of the Whitby Harbour Remediation Project in the Whitby Small Craft Harbour. The sediment remediation approach planned for the Site is hydraulic dredging with vacuum consolidation or other appropriate sediment de-watering method followed by offsite disposal at an external permitted landfill.
